<p>Sophie Sleigh-Johnson is a writer, artist and musician. She is the author of Chthonic Index - in collaboration with Simon Martin and Timothy Martin - published in 2015. She is currently working on a PhD at Goldsmiths. Recent projects include Cealdwiellla with New Noveta, and Machine of Instant Utility at Cabinet Gallery (group show). She occasionally broadcasts Chthonic Live on Resonance 104.4 FM, and she lives in Southend-On-Sea, Essex. â€“ sophiesleigh-johnson.co.uk</p>

